# 🥛 Prakritik – The Honest Dairy Experience

**Pure. Personal. Purposeful. Proven.**  
Prakritik is a clean, responsive web application designed to showcase the identity of an organic dairy brand. It promotes eco-conscious living and offers users an elegant view of products and the brand’s mission.

![Prakritik Banner](https://prakritik-web-app-git-main-aryans-projects-7f775849.vercel.app/banner.png) <!-- Replace with actual image if available -->

---

## 🌿 Live Demo

👉 [View Live Site](https://prakritik-web-app-git-main-aryans-projects-7f775849.vercel.app/)

---

## 🔧 Tech Stack

- 🧱 HTML5 & CSS3
- 🎨 Vanilla JavaScript
- 🚀 Deployed with [Vercel](https://vercel.com)

---

## ✨ Features

- 📱 **Responsive Design** – Works seamlessly across mobile, tablet, and desktop.
- 🌱 **Eco-friendly Theme** – A design reflecting the purity and simplicity of nature.
- 🛒 **Product Showcase** – Highlight organic dairy offerings.
- 📢 **Mission-Centered Content** – Clearly communicates the brand’s values and philosophy.
- 📬 **Contact Section** – Lets users reach out easily.

---

## 🖥️ Getting Started Locally

To run this project on your local machine:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/prakritik-web-app.git
cd prakritik-web-app
# Open index.html directly in your browser or use Live Server in VS Code
